params.markdown:
#### Cyera
   
**Classification**     

This dashboard provides visibility into classification data stream of Cyera, showing how sensitive data is categorized and tracked. It highlights classifications by sensitivity, data category and context tokenization, the total number of classifications, and trends of classification records over time. It also surfaces the top context roles associated with classified data and presents an essential details view with key metadata to support compliance and analysis.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/cyera/overview)**
